channel.title: Kicoh Remix Contest! [CLOSED]
channel.description:
Hi there! If you have not seen by the title, I am hosting a remix contest for my track kicoh!
The submissions for the remix will be due at the end of April! So 30th of April! 2018!
I will be selecting the winner on the 10th of May!
Here is the cover art, however you do not have to use it as your cover!
![M|500x500](upload://3FeM7E9QtRGTmtXaJh6zl0sbXSM.jpg)
It is advised that you listen to the original first so you don’t make a similar track to mine!
Original track: https://soundcloud.com/matikauxy/kicoh
Project file: [Remix has now been concluded.]
Have fun!! If you have any questions, feel free to dm me or in this thread! :matik:
The winner of this contest will be reposted by me on my Soundcloud, and also get a $25 iTunes gift card!
I will also be reposting some of my personal favourites of the remixes who almost got first place.
The other remixes will be put in a playlist.

It’s time! I’ve had some really tough decisions to make since there were so many good submissions, but I have finally decided!!

@niilo!!!

You can check out his track here.

If you would like feedback I can dm you what I liked best about your remix. This also goes to other remixers who want to know why they weren’t chosen to be the winner.

item.title: Kicoh Remix Contest! [CLOSED]
item.dc:creator: Matik
item.description:
Okay so good news! (for you at least ) Apple.com doesn’t send cards lower than $25.
The card price will not affect anyone because all I have to do is select the region I want to pay the card in which makes it easier for me to send it through rather than having it be Australian dollars and whoever the winner is gets an uneven amount.

So I’ll be deciding personally if I should keep my original idea of having it as AUD and the winner gets an uneven amount of money, or if I should choose to have the designated region of the winner.

So for now, the prize is a like, repost and a $25 iTunes Gift card of your country.

Anyways, good luck to the rest of the participants! You have 13 more days before the deadline! I will be deciding who gets first place about a week after the contest ends.

Read full topic
